{"tid":1318394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非 最後和平手段","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T14:12:20.000Z","uid":181165,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bce25c2edc224265bb4d35e28a3a502ccecb697e","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:34:47.000Z","msg":"經過琴日 開左個頭<br />\n往後落去<br />\n就算和理非遊行<br />\n班黑警都會照打<br />\n<br />\n班黑警死幾多我都無所謂 仲開心<br />\n但自己友 一個都不能少 <br />\n唔想再有人比屈斷手 插眼<br />\n<br />\n而問題嘅根源就係黑警犯用暴力<br />\n<br />\n唯一解決方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化黑警</span></span><br />\n<br />\n學共產黨果套 令警隊內部分裂<br />\n分開 黑警 同 真正嘅警察<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然唔知有冇。。。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果成功 呢場運動就見到曙光啦<br />\n因為警隊嘅武力 就係港共最後嘅防線<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n去警察宿舍/ 警處附近 貼posters, 開連農, 播片<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">切勿人少去</span> 可能有危險<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxzhRVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxzhRVN.png&h=993ca297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣傳需要時間<br />\n但盡早開始 愈好 <br />\n希望21號前 有成效<br />\n如果再嚟多次 勇武 前線兄弟 會傷好多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6月開始到依家 我地整左好多長輩圖<br />\n廢老 我地都同化到一堆<br />\n係時候搞一搞警察 同佢地 家人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">和平地</span><br />\n<br />\n黑警都係人 有負面情緒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">轉移晒去</span></span></span>警隊高層就岩"},{"pid":"bcbd160be21cc77dc1d15923297efee903af0cec","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"915d034a3207a48533c1b0fa14b702931c3c8a8f","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:40:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c66f1a55ea0b5825eeef62ea8c0ecb584e1414f3","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"唔係嘅 往後嘅示威遊行<br />\n都會向暴力 血腥方面發展<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好理想化 <br />\n但藉得一試"},{"pid":"6a2b6a465da5ba924dc160c4a3403a2a330cd534","tid":1318394,"uid":20723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c66f1a55ea0b5825eeef62ea8c0ecb584e1414f3","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"唔係嘅 往後嘅示威遊行<br />\n都會向暴力 血腥方面發展<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然好理想化 <br />\n但藉得一試"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TVnOYqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTVnOYqh.png&h=9aef83c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8W0PwY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8W0PwY.png&h=1fdcf126&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Y4qgbY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Y4qgbY.png&h=d66c50d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W20wWbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW20wWbZ.png&h=234b2f96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5819acc5af0b0404cd727e3f0b17d4567c3d8d1","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KFAMLur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKFAMLur.png&h=5d176682&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8878dd32e9e6f58360add8a3092afe7c57612ce","tid":1318394,"uid":181165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:19:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94828a8277999010f8ab63fff5f160ca374eb260","tid":1318394,"uid":